SECTION 3. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 49-3-105, is amended by designating
the existing language of subsection (c) as subdivision (c)(1) and adding the following as a new
subdivision (c)(2):
(2) A student generates a direct allocation for the LEA in which the student is a
member in the amount of fifty dollars ($50.00) for maintenance and infrastructure.
SECTION 4. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it,
and applies to the Tennessee investment in student achievement formula for the 2025-2026
school year and each school year thereafter.
